    <title>无人驾驶出租车动了谁的蛋糕</title>
    <link href="http://milkpku.github.io/blog/2024/07/14/%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E8%BD%A6%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%86%E8%B0%81%E7%9A%84%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95/"/>
    <id>http://milkpku.github.io/blog/2024/07/14/%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E8%BD%A6%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%86%E8%B0%81%E7%9A%84%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95/</id>
